WEBVTT

00:07.680 --> 00:08.960
‎SAY NO TO PIRACY, SUPPORT ORIGINALS

01:37.520 --> 01:42.960
‎ADAPTED FROM XI XING’S NOVEL
<i>‎QUEEN CHU</i>‎ ON QIDIAN.COM

02:02.160 --> 02:04.080
<i>His crime is unforgivable!</i>

02:04.160 --> 02:07.320
<i>Last night, he burned down</i>
<i>the Wei Village and killed 46 people!</i>

02:08.039 --> 02:10.160
Today, we will

02:10.240 --> 02:12.560
beat him to death in public

02:12.640 --> 02:15.280
to atone for his sins.

02:16.480 --> 02:17.400
<i>Sorry.</i>

02:17.480 --> 02:18.320
CAPITAL

02:18.400 --> 02:19.480
Because of me,

02:20.720 --> 02:22.120
you were also scolded by the elders.

02:22.640 --> 02:23.720
Don't be silly.

02:23.800 --> 02:26.400
As your brother, I must protect you.

02:26.480 --> 02:27.920
Sadly, this is too serious.

02:28.000 --> 02:29.880
Our elders are furious.

02:30.560 --> 02:31.880
Even as the head of our clan,

02:32.400 --> 02:33.640
I can't get you out of it.

02:36.960 --> 02:37.800
Yanlai,

02:39.240 --> 02:41.080
I believe you're innocent.

02:43.840 --> 02:44.840
Once I'm away,

02:46.680 --> 02:48.200
those elders won't come after you anymore.

02:48.800 --> 02:49.960
Where are you going?

02:51.320 --> 02:52.440
Any plans?

02:55.880 --> 02:57.200
This is a big world.

03:00.320 --> 03:02.280
I will always have somewhere to go.

03:03.560 --> 03:06.160
This secret elixir only belongs
to our direct line.

03:07.320 --> 03:08.760
It can even revive the dying.

03:09.840 --> 03:10.760
Keep it with you,

03:11.680 --> 03:13.000
in case of emergency.

03:33.040 --> 03:35.120
Sorry, sir. We're closed today.

03:35.200 --> 03:36.040
-Closed.
-Sorry.

03:36.120 --> 03:37.640
-Sorry for that.
-We're closed.

03:38.240 --> 03:41.200
Mr. Deng, the venison and roast pork
of Fenglin Restaurant

03:41.280 --> 03:42.520
are absolutely delicious.

03:43.040 --> 03:45.520
And have some meat soup.
That would be even better.

03:46.200 --> 03:47.120
How about…?

03:49.000 --> 03:50.160
I just need noodles.

03:52.920 --> 03:56.200
When the Yang and Zhao Clans
held great power as imperial in-laws,

03:57.000 --> 03:58.080
a single meal of theirs

03:58.160 --> 04:00.960
would feed an ordinary family
for an entire year.

04:01.480 --> 04:04.480
This gives a glimpse of the extravagance
of the imperial in-laws in power.

04:04.560 --> 04:05.680
Mr. Deng,

04:05.760 --> 04:08.720
we must bring down the Xie Clan.

04:08.800 --> 04:10.600
Yes. Yes, exactly.

04:10.680 --> 04:13.720
We can't let them rise
like the Yang and Zhao Clans.

04:15.080 --> 04:17.399
I wish they would rise
like the Yang and Zhao Clans.

04:17.480 --> 04:19.680
The rebellion of the Third Prince,

04:19.760 --> 04:22.720
the young emperor,
and the foreign invasion…

04:22.800 --> 04:23.800
The root cause

04:24.320 --> 04:26.360
was the trouble of imperial in-laws.

04:26.440 --> 04:28.160
Now, common folks

04:28.240 --> 04:29.760
hate them a lot.

04:31.040 --> 04:32.440
Once the Xie Clan oversteps,

04:32.520 --> 04:35.000
even their reputation over a century

04:35.080 --> 04:36.560
won't make anyone forgive them.

04:38.720 --> 04:41.120
It makes sense, Mr. Deng. It makes sense.

04:43.240 --> 04:45.640
Xie Yanfang is cunning

04:45.720 --> 04:46.800
and sophisticated.

04:46.880 --> 04:49.000
He excels at seeking good fame.

04:49.080 --> 04:51.280
Now, he's the Emperor's uncle.

04:51.360 --> 04:53.960
Many people entrust him

04:54.040 --> 04:54.880
with state affairs.

04:54.960 --> 04:56.840
His reputation has grown.

04:56.920 --> 05:00.560
But the Xie Clan
has more than just Xie Yanfang.

05:00.640 --> 05:03.400
Leaving others aside,
his brother, Xie Yanlai,

05:04.960 --> 05:08.960
behaves quite arrogantly,
just like the Yang and Zhao Clans.

05:09.800 --> 05:12.000
Well, Xie Yanlai is quite extraordinary.

05:12.960 --> 05:14.640
He can even manipulate His Majesty.

05:14.720 --> 05:17.320
I would rather say

05:18.240 --> 05:20.440
someone else manipulates His Majesty.

05:22.000 --> 05:24.280
The Grand Princess
does not trust Xie Yanfang.

05:24.880 --> 05:26.400
But she shows Xie Yanlai

05:26.920 --> 05:28.160
special favor.

05:28.760 --> 05:30.320
And why is that?

05:31.200 --> 05:32.400
Maybe

05:34.360 --> 05:36.480
she wants to raise up a new imperial uncle

05:37.080 --> 05:38.480
to cause infighting.

05:39.800 --> 05:41.520
When brothers turn against each other,

05:41.600 --> 05:43.880
a fight for status would be the worst.

05:43.960 --> 05:46.480
Xie Yanlai is favored
and supported by the Grand Princess.

05:46.560 --> 05:49.200
If he fights for power,

05:49.280 --> 05:52.360
Xie Yanfang will surely have a headache.

05:57.000 --> 05:58.040
Father.

05:59.400 --> 06:00.440
Father.

06:01.720 --> 06:05.120
Our spy's latest report says
Chu Ling has been unconscious for days.

06:05.800 --> 06:06.920
He's probably dying.

06:08.600 --> 06:09.680
Xun,

06:10.520 --> 06:12.360
look at the alchemy fire behind me.

06:13.440 --> 06:14.480
Spiritual elixirs can only be done

06:15.320 --> 06:16.560
by slow simmering.

06:16.640 --> 06:19.320
An intense fire will end in vain.

06:19.400 --> 06:22.040
Your rash alliance
with the Northern Desert at Wangcheng

06:22.120 --> 06:23.360
utterly failed.

06:23.440 --> 06:25.240
Do you realize your fault?

06:25.320 --> 06:26.520
Father,

06:26.600 --> 06:29.440
I had a perfect plan
for the battle of Wangcheng.

06:30.080 --> 06:31.600
But Chu Zhao interfered.

06:33.120 --> 06:35.400
Once something goes wrong,
your plan cannot be branded as perfect.

06:40.920 --> 06:41.840
Father,

06:42.800 --> 06:43.920
fortunately,

06:44.440 --> 06:47.720
I eliminated their remnants.
No future threats will be left.

06:48.560 --> 06:49.560
Don't worry, Father.

06:56.800 --> 06:59.080
How many times have I told you?

07:00.080 --> 07:03.040
To seek great things,
you must behave like the stove fire.

07:03.800 --> 07:04.880
You should stay patient

07:04.960 --> 07:06.720
until the right moment comes.

07:07.320 --> 07:08.800
I don't quite agree.

07:10.360 --> 07:13.720
The war between the two states
has been going on for days,

07:13.800 --> 07:15.280
but it's not intense.

07:15.360 --> 07:17.000
Victory reports in the Capital

07:17.520 --> 07:18.680
make people feel

07:18.760 --> 07:20.720
that the Northern Desert
is merely bluffing.

07:21.320 --> 07:22.440
Actually, that's not true.

07:22.520 --> 07:24.400
The Northern Desert Royal Army

07:24.920 --> 07:25.760
has been waiting

07:25.840 --> 07:28.360
for a chance to strike a fatal blow.

07:29.760 --> 07:32.080
The chance is the death of Chu Ling.

07:32.600 --> 07:34.160
You're being too impatient.

07:34.840 --> 07:38.240
Northern Desert foes are treacherous.
They aren't a reliable ally.

07:38.320 --> 07:39.440
Father,

07:39.520 --> 07:41.520
let me lead troops to Yunzhong.

07:42.960 --> 07:45.520
The Royal Army has gathered and departed.

07:45.600 --> 07:48.120
They're determined to win this battle.

07:48.720 --> 07:50.720
Chu Ling is on his last legs.

07:51.400 --> 07:52.560
He won't live long.

07:53.400 --> 07:55.080
It's time for us to turn the tide.

07:56.280 --> 07:57.840
Even if Chu Ling dies,

07:59.440 --> 08:01.840
his army can still fight a war.

08:02.440 --> 08:03.720
What you should do

08:04.440 --> 08:05.920
is to lead troops to the Capital

08:08.000 --> 08:09.080
and guard the Emperor.

08:14.360 --> 08:15.360
Yes.

08:34.640 --> 08:36.400
-Go get Mr. Zhong.
-Yes.

08:43.760 --> 08:45.560
Zhao, scouts reported

08:45.640 --> 08:48.760
the Northern Desert Royal Army
passed Heishui Ridge

08:48.840 --> 08:50.720
and is less than a hundred li away.

08:50.800 --> 08:52.840
Beacon towers along the way were ruined.

08:52.920 --> 08:54.400
I'm afraid they'll arrive very soon.

08:54.480 --> 08:56.840
We must make early plans.

08:58.000 --> 09:01.080
Looks like their king knows
about Father's condition.

09:03.760 --> 09:04.960
He knows the time has come.

09:05.640 --> 09:07.880
The General's condition
has been kept secret.

09:07.960 --> 09:08.960
I don't know why…

09:09.040 --> 09:11.400
Nothing stays hidden forever.

09:13.080 --> 09:15.040
Now, there's no need

09:16.160 --> 09:17.200
to hunt for spies.

09:25.640 --> 09:28.360
Since their king
has led the troops himself,

09:29.920 --> 09:31.800
I will command our troops

09:33.080 --> 09:34.480
to fight them

09:35.760 --> 09:37.120
on behalf of my father.

09:38.520 --> 09:39.920
The commander's absence from the war

09:41.840 --> 09:43.800
will surely affect the army's morale.

09:46.080 --> 09:47.480
If a woman like me

09:48.360 --> 09:50.400
took command in her father's place,

09:51.840 --> 09:53.240
the result wouldn't be as good.

09:55.360 --> 09:56.200
But luckily,

09:57.240 --> 09:59.640
I'm not only Chu Ling's daughter,

10:00.600 --> 10:03.080
but also the Grand Princess of State.

10:04.040 --> 10:05.800
Heed my order, Zhong Changrong.

10:06.720 --> 10:07.560
Yes.

10:08.080 --> 10:09.840
Prepare the Grand Princess's procession.

10:12.840 --> 10:14.120
We'll set out for war.

10:20.960 --> 10:22.920
The secrets of Xie Clan of Gaoyang

10:23.440 --> 10:26.040
are indeed more spectacular
than I imagined.

10:26.640 --> 10:28.120
All who surrender,

10:28.200 --> 10:29.400
for any reason,

10:30.080 --> 10:32.160
shall be executed immediately

10:32.240 --> 10:33.960
and excluded from the ancestral graves.

10:34.760 --> 10:36.120
The Xie's secret elixir

10:36.640 --> 10:38.600
can bring the dead back to life.

10:39.280 --> 10:40.840
It's kept by the clan head.

10:41.360 --> 10:42.920
Only the direct line can see it.

10:45.680 --> 10:47.880
Bring the dead back to life?

10:50.520 --> 10:51.480
How interesting.

10:54.400 --> 10:56.200
Knowing that my father is gravely ill,

10:56.280 --> 10:58.200
400,000 Northern Desert troops came up,

10:58.280 --> 10:59.520
trying to capture Yunzhong.

11:06.040 --> 11:07.080
Mr. Zhong,

11:07.160 --> 11:09.760
you lead main troops
to confront the enemy's main force.

11:10.360 --> 11:11.200
Yes.

11:12.760 --> 11:14.440
-I'll go with Zhong.
-No.

11:15.040 --> 11:17.640
You take the Vanguard Battalion
to charge out from the left wing,

11:17.720 --> 11:18.560
go through Yingzui Valley,

11:19.160 --> 11:21.200
and circle around to the enemy's rear.

11:21.720 --> 11:23.320
You and Mr. Zhong launch a pincer attack

11:23.400 --> 11:24.960
to break up the enemy's assault.

11:25.560 --> 11:26.400
Yes.

11:27.000 --> 11:29.040
If you fail this mission,
you'll be punished.

11:30.360 --> 11:33.320
Yingzui Valley is vital.
Our enemies also know that.

11:33.400 --> 11:35.520
-They'll guard it with massive forces.
-I take your order.

11:39.240 --> 11:40.800
I pledge to take Yingzui Valley.

11:41.640 --> 11:42.480
Move out now.

11:43.080 --> 11:43.920
-Yes.
-Yes.

11:44.000 --> 11:46.600
We swear to live and die for Yunzhong.

11:47.200 --> 11:48.040
In this battle,

11:48.560 --> 11:50.440
I will make our enemies know

11:50.960 --> 11:53.400
that we will never yield a single inch
of our own territory.

12:03.720 --> 12:05.400
YUNZHONG

12:41.200 --> 12:44.240
When our state is in turmoil,

12:44.840 --> 12:45.960
our late Emperor is gone,

12:46.480 --> 12:49.800
and our new emperor is still young,
the Northern Desert invades our frontier

12:50.480 --> 12:51.720
and slaughters our people.

12:51.800 --> 12:54.080
As the Grand Princess of State,

12:54.600 --> 12:56.840
I must protect all the people.

12:56.920 --> 12:58.240
In the name

12:59.000 --> 13:01.840
of the Grand Princess of State,
I condemn the Northern Desert.

13:01.920 --> 13:03.800
Those who invade our land…

13:03.880 --> 13:04.720
Kill them!

13:05.320 --> 13:06.920
Those who butcher our people…

13:07.000 --> 13:07.840
Kill them!

13:08.600 --> 13:09.880
Soldiers,

13:10.400 --> 13:12.240
follow me in killing the enemies!

13:13.200 --> 13:14.960
We'll defend our territory

13:16.040 --> 13:17.680
and guard our people!

13:17.760 --> 13:22.920
-Kill!
-Kill!

13:23.000 --> 13:26.720
-Kill!
-Kill!

13:27.320 --> 13:31.240
-Kill!
-Kill!

13:31.320 --> 13:32.120
Let's kill!

13:36.840 --> 13:37.680
Charge!

13:43.960 --> 13:46.000
Charge!

13:50.440 --> 13:53.560
YINGZUI VALLEY

14:11.720 --> 14:12.560
How dare

14:13.480 --> 14:15.000
those northern foes invade our land!

14:15.080 --> 14:16.560
-Don't die.
-You either.

15:09.920 --> 15:11.360
At this rate, we can't hold on.

15:11.440 --> 15:14.160
Without reinforcements, we'll lose.
Hold on, all of you!

15:14.680 --> 15:17.400
Frontier soldiers like us would rather
die on the battlefield!

15:33.320 --> 15:34.800
The Grand Princess of State.

15:34.880 --> 15:38.880
Anyone who kills the Grand Princess
will win a title.

15:38.960 --> 15:41.160
Kill!

15:55.320 --> 15:56.160
Why are you here?

15:56.240 --> 15:58.080
To do what a mother should do.

15:58.160 --> 16:00.120
You've suffered heavy casualties.

16:00.200 --> 16:01.960
Unless you break through here,

16:02.040 --> 16:04.480
even the reinforcements
will be trapped and killed at this pass.

16:04.560 --> 16:06.040
It's Alan Ruoying.

16:06.920 --> 16:09.320
The traitor our king
has been hunting for 19 years.

16:09.400 --> 16:10.760
How come she's here?

16:10.840 --> 16:12.320
Catch Alan Ruoying alive!

16:22.120 --> 16:22.960
I still failed

16:23.560 --> 16:26.520
to be the perfect mother in your heart.

16:28.920 --> 16:30.000
I'm sorry.

16:31.520 --> 16:34.200
I can find a way to break through.
Don't do anything stupid!

16:34.280 --> 16:36.760
That day, you said
you would grant me a reward.

16:37.880 --> 16:39.800
Now, I'm asking for this reward.

16:45.320 --> 16:46.480
I want you to live.

16:48.520 --> 16:50.600
You want to know
how I've been all these years.

16:51.640 --> 16:54.480
You also want to know
if I have forgiven you.

16:55.400 --> 16:56.640
If you die,

16:57.400 --> 16:59.400
you will never know the answers.

17:06.520 --> 17:08.000
Actually, I know.

17:11.200 --> 17:12.319
I've always known.

17:12.920 --> 17:14.280
No!

17:14.880 --> 17:16.040
Mother!

17:16.680 --> 17:17.640
Don't go!

17:18.160 --> 17:19.960
Don't leave me alone!

17:25.760 --> 17:26.680
Mother!

17:44.240 --> 17:46.160
Mother!

19:12.320 --> 19:13.240
General.

19:13.320 --> 19:16.080
It's the General.
He's beating the drum to cheer us on!

19:28.760 --> 19:32.000
Kill!

19:32.960 --> 19:34.520
My mother

19:36.120 --> 19:37.800
asked me to live.

19:38.360 --> 19:40.040
Soldiers, on my command!

19:40.920 --> 19:43.560
-Kill!
-Kill!

20:00.680 --> 20:01.840
<i>‎Listen to the roar of battle.</i>

20:04.280 --> 20:05.760
Her Highness is as good as you, General.

20:06.600 --> 20:08.600
She's fighting alongside Jiu
to kill the enemies.

20:19.040 --> 20:20.080
Zhao,

20:21.560 --> 20:24.280
you must stay alive.

21:15.840 --> 21:16.880
General…

21:18.200 --> 21:20.360
General!

21:29.520 --> 21:30.920
Father.

21:31.000 --> 21:31.960
We…

21:51.400 --> 21:52.760
-General.
-General.

22:42.880 --> 22:43.720
Father.

22:46.480 --> 22:48.160
We won.

22:59.080 --> 23:00.120
The General

23:01.560 --> 23:02.760
died on the battlefield

23:03.680 --> 23:05.240
the way he wished.

23:14.000 --> 23:15.040
Zhao.

23:22.120 --> 23:23.040
All of you, leave us.

23:24.800 --> 23:25.640
-Yes.
-Yes.

23:53.920 --> 23:55.400
Mu Mianhong blasted open

23:57.800 --> 23:59.480
the pass at Yingzui Valley for us.

24:11.840 --> 24:13.280
Father didn't lie to me.

24:16.680 --> 24:18.160
My mother

24:19.840 --> 24:21.920
is the best woman in the world.

24:24.000 --> 24:25.000
She's kind

24:26.840 --> 24:27.840
and brave,

24:29.600 --> 24:30.760
and she loves me.

24:33.520 --> 24:34.760
Mr. Zhong,

24:37.360 --> 24:38.440
my mother…

24:40.600 --> 24:42.040
She loves me.

24:43.160 --> 24:45.560
She protected me with her own life.

24:46.480 --> 24:47.320
Zhao,

24:47.400 --> 24:49.680
if you feel sad,

24:49.760 --> 24:51.320
let it all out.

24:51.920 --> 24:52.920
Sad?

24:53.960 --> 24:55.120
I'm not sad.

24:59.080 --> 25:01.720
My father watched us defeat our enemies.

25:02.960 --> 25:03.960
And now,

25:05.040 --> 25:06.400
he and my mother

25:07.160 --> 25:08.680
can be reunited in the underworld.

25:10.200 --> 25:12.880
They no longer need
to worry about mortal affairs.

25:14.880 --> 25:16.200
I feel happy for them.

25:40.000 --> 25:41.120
Make an announcement.

25:41.200 --> 25:43.160
Guard General Chu Ling

25:46.080 --> 25:46.920
passed away.

25:48.800 --> 25:49.920
Now?

25:50.440 --> 25:51.360
Is it appropriate?

25:51.440 --> 25:53.960
The Northern Desert King lost and fled,

25:54.040 --> 25:55.440
but the war isn't over yet.

25:56.040 --> 25:58.320
If we announce the General's death now,

25:59.120 --> 26:00.680
will our soldiers lose heart?

26:00.760 --> 26:02.200
Now is the time.

26:04.120 --> 26:05.440
We should let them know

26:06.840 --> 26:09.160
the General has fought with them
and died in battle.

26:11.920 --> 26:13.240
A general like him,

26:13.840 --> 26:15.120
even when he's gone,

26:16.880 --> 26:19.160
the soldiers will believe
he's still there for them.

26:20.360 --> 26:22.520
Even if the enemies return at once,

26:23.480 --> 26:24.920
they will be fearless.

26:27.600 --> 26:29.960
My father used the last of his strength

26:30.480 --> 26:32.080
to repel the enemies.

26:33.720 --> 26:35.240
When we announce his death now,

26:36.520 --> 26:38.320
grief shall turn into strength

26:39.320 --> 26:40.760
instead of panic.

26:43.200 --> 26:44.480
We're fearless.

26:45.480 --> 26:47.120
We're invincible.

26:52.320 --> 26:53.400
Our state

26:54.200 --> 26:55.320
will win!

27:06.960 --> 27:10.960
-Guard General Chu Ling! Farewell!
-Guard General Chu Ling! Farewell!

27:11.040 --> 27:15.280
-Guard General Chu Ling! Farewell!
-Guard General Chu Ling! Farewell!

27:15.880 --> 27:19.240
-Guard General Chu Ling! Farewell!
-Guard General Chu Ling! Farewell!

27:27.040 --> 27:30.280
-Guard General Chu Ling! Farewell!
-Guard General Chu Ling! Farewell!

27:30.360 --> 27:33.520
-Guard General Chu Ling! Farewell!
-Guard General Chu Ling! Farewell!

28:23.560 --> 28:26.120
You haven't slept for three days.
Are you torturing yourself?

28:36.560 --> 28:37.400
I'm sorry.

28:38.960 --> 28:39.800
Satisfied, huh?

28:48.120 --> 28:49.520
Why must you push me?

28:49.600 --> 28:51.520
Must you see how I break down?

28:52.200 --> 28:53.440
Xie Yanlai,

28:53.520 --> 28:56.680
does it make you happy
when you crush my composure?

29:02.520 --> 29:04.120
Do you know why I can't close my eyes?

29:05.400 --> 29:06.520
Because when I close my eyes,

29:07.520 --> 29:09.800
I see how my mother
sacrificed her life before me.

29:11.240 --> 29:12.800
And I see

29:13.840 --> 29:15.720
how my father passed away
with his eyes still open.

29:17.400 --> 29:18.840
How am I supposed to face this?

29:20.000 --> 29:21.640
How can I not hate or feel pain?

29:22.320 --> 29:23.760
It's your fault. He could have lived.

29:23.840 --> 29:26.120
Even if he remained feeble,
he could at least be alive!

29:26.920 --> 29:29.560
If he lived, I wouldn't be an orphan.

29:29.640 --> 29:31.280
You're the murderer.

29:31.800 --> 29:33.280
My mother died before me,

29:33.800 --> 29:35.840
and you killed my father. It's you!

30:03.480 --> 30:04.400
Zhao.

30:23.080 --> 30:23.920
Mr. Deng,

30:24.000 --> 30:25.840
we looked into the Xie's secret elixir.

30:30.920 --> 30:32.160
It's the Bloodburn Pill.

30:32.240 --> 30:34.120
It's peculiarly poisonous.

30:34.200 --> 30:36.840
Its power to revive the dead is a fraud.

30:36.920 --> 30:38.200
Every time it is used,

30:38.280 --> 30:39.480
death comes closer.

30:40.600 --> 30:42.320
The bloodburn energy

30:43.440 --> 30:44.760
has a supernatural effect,

30:45.400 --> 30:46.800
so it takes a supernatural cost.

30:47.840 --> 30:49.520
Everything in this world

30:50.040 --> 30:51.840
has been destined.

30:59.320 --> 31:00.400
Three years ago,

31:00.920 --> 31:02.960
Chu Ling was badly injured in a battle.

31:03.040 --> 31:05.600
He healed quickly
and won battles in the next year

31:05.680 --> 31:06.560
as if he were blessed.

31:07.160 --> 31:08.600
Yet his body kept getting worse.

31:08.680 --> 31:10.320
He coughed up blood and went blind.

31:10.400 --> 31:13.200
No one around him except Xie Yanlai

31:13.280 --> 31:15.160
was able to do that.

31:15.880 --> 31:17.360
This can't possibly be a coincidence.

31:17.440 --> 31:19.560
Are you saying

31:20.080 --> 31:21.080
the Xie Family

31:21.800 --> 31:22.920
poisoned Chu Ling?

31:23.680 --> 31:25.840
I wonder how the Grand Princess

31:25.920 --> 31:28.240
will feel when she knows

31:28.320 --> 31:29.920
her most trusted Xie Yanlai

31:30.880 --> 31:32.360
poisoned her father.

31:33.920 --> 31:35.280
Announcement from the frontier!

31:35.360 --> 31:36.960
Guard General Chu Ling passed away!

31:37.040 --> 31:38.600
Announcement from the frontier!

31:39.200 --> 31:40.840
Guard General Chu Ling passed away!

31:41.360 --> 31:43.000
Announcement from the frontier!

31:43.080 --> 31:45.160
-Guard General Chu Ling passed away!
-Shao You.

31:46.440 --> 31:47.440
Guess.

31:49.080 --> 31:51.880
Can we use the death of the God of War

31:52.560 --> 31:55.240
to uproot the Xie Clan
from their century-old power?

31:56.480 --> 31:57.960
Go spread the news.

31:58.880 --> 32:00.480
Make sure everyone knows it.

32:01.720 --> 32:02.560
Yes.

32:08.200 --> 32:10.520
His Lordship is right. Chu Ling is gone,

32:11.040 --> 32:13.520
but it's still hard to invade Yunzhong.

32:13.600 --> 32:15.520
Luckily, you took his advice

32:15.600 --> 32:16.440
not to act rashly.

32:17.760 --> 32:20.000
Once again, they ruined

32:20.520 --> 32:21.480
such a great chance.

32:21.560 --> 32:22.920
Calm down.

32:23.440 --> 32:24.680
We'll find another chance.

32:27.360 --> 32:28.920
Chu Ling is dead.

32:29.880 --> 32:31.080
Under such circumstances,

32:32.080 --> 32:34.480
Xie Yanlai is most likely
to take over his troops.

32:35.440 --> 32:36.600
Xie Yanlai

32:37.200 --> 32:39.400
ruined your plan at Cangmu Stronghold

32:39.480 --> 32:41.600
and then helped Chu Zhao
defeat the enemies.

32:41.680 --> 32:44.840
If he takes command,
he'll be a huge threat.

32:50.960 --> 32:52.000
Tie Ying.

32:54.520 --> 32:55.520
Think about it.

32:56.040 --> 32:58.960
Rumors that Chu Ling
was killed by the Xie's secret elixir

33:00.080 --> 33:01.320
have spread to the Capital.

33:03.360 --> 33:06.320
Chu Ling enjoyed immense prestige
in Yunzhong.

33:07.080 --> 33:08.160
Those frontier troops.

33:09.440 --> 33:11.880
Those common people under his protection.

33:14.760 --> 33:15.800
Tell me.

33:16.840 --> 33:18.680
Do you think Xie Yanlai, the murderer,

33:21.080 --> 33:22.800
can leave Yunzhong alive?

33:23.520 --> 33:24.520
In my opinion,

33:25.040 --> 33:27.480
he can't. Frontier folks are loyal.

33:27.560 --> 33:30.200
If they believe
Xie Yanlai poisoned General Chu…

33:32.120 --> 33:33.000
Good.

33:34.000 --> 33:35.160
Very good.

33:36.600 --> 33:39.240
Since rumors have reached the Capital,

33:40.600 --> 33:42.680
we'll add fuel to the fire.

33:43.480 --> 33:44.800
Spread the news to Yunzhong

33:45.320 --> 33:46.680
as quickly as possible.

33:48.080 --> 33:49.760
I can't wait to see

33:50.680 --> 33:53.760
how he gets crushed by angry people

33:54.520 --> 33:56.280
and perishes in misery.

33:56.360 --> 33:57.440
TAIJI HALL

33:57.520 --> 33:58.960
There are rumors

33:59.600 --> 34:02.160
that General Chu Ling was killed
by the Xie's secret elixir,

34:02.240 --> 34:03.600
the Bloodburn Pill.

34:04.560 --> 34:07.200
These mere rumors
have spread far and wide.

34:08.440 --> 34:10.719
Mr. Xie, what's your opinion?

34:10.800 --> 34:13.320
Mr. Deng, I'm not

34:13.400 --> 34:15.400
as well-informed as you.

34:16.440 --> 34:18.199
I didn't hear those rumors until today.

34:18.800 --> 34:20.440
Then, ministers,

34:20.960 --> 34:24.239
what do you think when one single clan

34:24.840 --> 34:26.159
has such poison?

34:27.080 --> 34:28.840
General Chu Ling died.

34:28.920 --> 34:32.960
Who knows if one of us
will be poisoned next?

34:35.400 --> 34:37.440
Mr. Deng has a point.

34:37.520 --> 34:40.199
If someone evil uses such poison,

34:40.280 --> 34:42.120
the consequences would be terrible.

34:42.199 --> 34:44.080
It makes sense, Censor.

34:45.639 --> 34:48.120
But lately, I've heard
about something fun.

34:49.120 --> 34:51.120
Mr. Deng is keeping

34:52.480 --> 34:54.480
the late Emperor's relics.

34:55.239 --> 34:56.080
Mr. Deng,

34:56.600 --> 34:58.240
what do you have to say?

34:59.800 --> 35:00.840
Mr. Xie,

35:00.920 --> 35:02.600
how can you

35:03.600 --> 35:06.120
make irresponsible remarks
about the late Emperor?

35:06.200 --> 35:08.200
You guessed groundlessly, too.

35:08.280 --> 35:10.120
How could you blame me

35:10.800 --> 35:12.240
for doing the same?

35:13.760 --> 35:14.720
That's right, Your Majesty.

35:14.800 --> 35:18.360
General Chu was in poor health
for a long time.

35:18.440 --> 35:21.720
Why did people suddenly say
he was poisoned?

35:21.800 --> 35:23.720
Even in that case,

35:23.800 --> 35:27.160
why did the Xie Family get involved?

35:27.240 --> 35:29.520
Victory news has just arrived.

35:29.600 --> 35:32.280
Frontier troops
are still fighting enemies.

35:32.360 --> 35:33.360
Mr. Deng,

35:33.440 --> 35:36.640
such rumors will break
the soldiers' hearts.

35:37.400 --> 35:40.680
As the saying goes,
nothing comes from nothing.

35:40.760 --> 35:44.040
Whether the Xie Family
has this secret elixir,

35:44.640 --> 35:46.200
Mr. Xie,

35:46.280 --> 35:49.160
you should know it perfectly.

35:49.240 --> 35:50.120
Your brother Xie Yanlai

35:50.200 --> 35:54.160
lurked by General Chu's side
for five years.

35:54.240 --> 35:55.560
There could be plenty of chances

35:55.640 --> 35:57.760
that he could poison the General.

35:59.520 --> 36:00.560
Stop arguing!

36:01.320 --> 36:02.440
Our enemies have just retreated.

36:03.040 --> 36:05.720
All parts of our state
should unite against them.

36:06.440 --> 36:07.960
I don't want to hear you argue.

36:08.880 --> 36:09.880
I just want to ask

36:10.960 --> 36:12.920
when my sister and my uncle

36:13.000 --> 36:14.320
will come back.

36:14.840 --> 36:15.760
Your Majesty,

36:15.840 --> 36:18.480
the Grand Princess
is in mourning for General Chu.

36:19.000 --> 36:21.320
When the war is over
and the funeral is done,

36:21.840 --> 36:23.200
she will come back.

36:23.920 --> 36:24.920
But…

36:25.600 --> 36:26.800
General Chu is gone.

36:26.880 --> 36:28.920
Let's not dwell

36:29.440 --> 36:32.000
on a lady's mourning for her father.

36:32.600 --> 36:34.520
General Chu is a pillar of our state.

36:34.600 --> 36:37.000
He deserves generous rewards.

36:37.520 --> 36:38.920
Even when he's dead,

36:39.000 --> 36:40.760
to boost morale,

36:40.840 --> 36:42.520
frontier troops who won this battle

36:42.600 --> 36:45.320
should be rewarded.

36:45.400 --> 36:46.240
It makes sense.

36:47.080 --> 36:48.960
General Chu is our backbone.

36:49.040 --> 36:50.760
He deserves a national funeral.

36:51.520 --> 36:52.720
Wise decision, Your Majesty.

36:53.960 --> 36:56.040
Mr. Xie, you really

36:57.120 --> 36:58.720
prioritize the greater good.

37:05.920 --> 37:07.400
How long

37:07.920 --> 37:09.040
do you think

37:09.640 --> 37:10.760
this secret can be kept?

37:11.640 --> 37:13.200
If you're so confident,

37:14.040 --> 37:15.560
why don't you ask my brother

37:16.320 --> 37:17.960
when he comes back?

37:20.040 --> 37:20.960
Oh.

37:21.880 --> 37:23.680
The coffin from the Grand Princess…

37:24.360 --> 37:26.040
You can have it sent to Yunzhong

37:26.120 --> 37:29.080
for General Chu to express your sorrow.

37:31.840 --> 37:33.400
That's golden-thread nanmu, after all.

37:35.360 --> 37:37.280
You wouldn't be reluctant, would you?

38:03.040 --> 38:05.480
After only a few minutes,
you can't read anymore.

38:06.240 --> 38:08.560
Those dense words

38:09.440 --> 38:11.400
give me a headache.

38:12.240 --> 38:13.240
Father,

38:14.160 --> 38:15.560
shall we talk?

38:17.520 --> 38:18.640
About what?

38:18.720 --> 38:21.560
Tell me more about my mother.

38:38.840 --> 38:40.960
Father.

38:41.040 --> 38:43.680
Father.

38:50.920 --> 38:51.960
Are you hurt?

39:01.840 --> 39:02.680
Do you like it?

39:04.040 --> 39:05.640
Greetings, Lady General.

39:32.360 --> 39:33.960
I miss you so much.

39:43.080 --> 39:43.960
Zhao,

39:44.680 --> 39:46.920
I know you don't want to hear me out.

39:47.680 --> 39:48.720
But…

39:49.920 --> 39:52.040
it's unfair to Jiu.

39:56.720 --> 39:59.440
People say your father is the God of War

39:59.520 --> 40:00.560
who never loses a battle.

40:00.640 --> 40:02.600
As long as Chu Ling is around,

40:02.680 --> 40:04.560
the frontier will always be peaceful.

40:05.880 --> 40:07.720
But he's just an ordinary man.

40:08.240 --> 40:10.000
He got injured,

40:10.080 --> 40:11.880
fell sick, and died.

40:12.840 --> 40:13.840
<i>Three years ago,</i>

40:14.360 --> 40:15.280
<i>in the Battle of the Frontier River,</i>

40:16.080 --> 40:17.360
-<i>your father was shot by a poisoned arrow</i>
-Doctors!

40:17.440 --> 40:19.200
-<i>and nearly lost his life.</i>
-Doctors, help!

40:19.280 --> 40:21.520
<i>At that time,</i>

40:22.120 --> 40:24.000
<i>Jiu took out this pill.</i>

40:25.320 --> 40:26.920
The arrow has
the Northern Desert's poison!

40:27.960 --> 40:29.080
Any antidote?

40:29.160 --> 40:30.560
The toxin is inside him.

40:30.640 --> 40:32.160
I'll purge it first.

40:33.600 --> 40:35.920
But General, you must rest very well

40:36.000 --> 40:37.360
instead of going to war again.

40:37.440 --> 40:39.840
Otherwise, the remaining toxin
will spread all over,

40:39.920 --> 40:41.080
and you won't live.

40:41.160 --> 40:43.960
The war is urgent. It can't do without me.

40:44.040 --> 40:45.000
No, General.

40:45.080 --> 40:46.400
You're too weak to go to war again.

40:46.480 --> 40:50.120
I would rather die on the battlefield.

40:50.200 --> 40:52.920
-How could I just stay bedridden?
-General.

40:53.000 --> 40:54.240
-General.
-I rather die…

40:54.320 --> 40:56.440
Secret elixir from the Xie Clan.
A pill can revive the dying.

40:57.200 --> 40:58.040
Will you try it?

40:59.440 --> 41:01.760
Where did you get this pill?

41:02.360 --> 41:04.160
From my brother, before I left home.

41:04.240 --> 41:05.520
He wouldn't harm me.

41:06.320 --> 41:08.280
General, let me test it.

41:08.360 --> 41:09.520
There's no time for it.

41:10.200 --> 41:11.560
As long as it works,

41:12.280 --> 41:15.160
I will take it, even if it's poison.

41:16.080 --> 41:17.040
<i>Your father took it</i>

41:17.120 --> 41:19.240
<i>as his last hope.</i>

41:19.320 --> 41:21.120
To save his life,

41:21.640 --> 41:23.680
we had no choice but to take that risk.

41:24.440 --> 41:25.320
Anyway,

41:25.400 --> 41:27.720
without Jiu's pill,

41:28.320 --> 41:29.960
the General would have died that day.

41:34.600 --> 41:36.080
I, Zhong Changrong,

41:36.600 --> 41:38.520
swear on my life.

41:38.600 --> 41:41.000
When Jiu offered the pill,

41:41.080 --> 41:42.360
he told us his true identity

41:42.440 --> 41:45.000
instead of hiding anything.

41:45.080 --> 41:47.400
The General was almost dying,

41:47.480 --> 41:50.000
and we had to take that risk.

41:50.720 --> 41:51.560
Report!

41:52.800 --> 41:54.120
Xie Yanlai is kneeling in public
to beg for forgiveness.

41:54.200 --> 41:55.520
Crowds have surrounded him.

41:55.600 --> 41:57.160
It's utter chaos out there.
